# The Sheena Archive

A digital fan archive dedicated to BINI Sheena.

## Goals

- Create a archive website.
- Build a responsive website.
- Add interactive games and features.
- Deploy the website for free.

## Progress

- [x] Project setup
- [x] Git initialized
- [x] First commit
- [x] Hero section started
- [x] Responsive layout
- [x] Timeline
- [ ] Gallery
- [x] Games
- [ ] Deployment




